00:18:00.312 --> 00:18:03.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, we will begin</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the extraction process for penicillin.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:18:03.816 --> 00:18:06.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>First, filter the culture</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>medium through a funnel.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:18:16.829 --> 00:18:21.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Next, pour rapeseed oil</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into the filtered liquid and mix well.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:18:22.101 --> 00:18:25.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This will cause the liquid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the container</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:18:25.537 --> 00:18:28.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>to separate the contents of the solution</i></c.bg_transparent>

218
00:18:28.207 --> 00:18:33.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>into three layers of water-soluble,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>fat-soluble, and insoluble contents.</i></c.bg_transparent>

219
00:18:33.946 --> 00:18:36.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Since penicillin is water-soluble,</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:18:36.181 --> 00:18:38.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we will extract only</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the water from this mixture.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:18:40.152 --> 00:18:42.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, the water contains penicillin?</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:18:42.855 --> 00:18:43.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Correct.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:18:44.323 --> 00:18:47.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>From here on, we need to remove</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>further impurities</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:18:47.459 --> 00:18:49.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from this penicillin solution.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:18:51.797 --> 00:18:53.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In this container,</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:18:53.132 --> 00:18:55.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we have crushed, sterilized charcoal.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:18:56.835 --> 00:19:00.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pour the penicillin solution into it,</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:19:00.639 --> 00:19:02.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and stir it again.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:19:06.111 --> 00:19:10.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The penicillin will absorb</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>onto the charcoal.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:19:11.917 --> 00:19:13.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pack the charcoal into a container,</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:19:13.585 --> 00:19:17.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>pass distilled pure water through it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to wash away the impurities.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:19:19.691 --> 00:19:23.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Next, pass acidic water</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>made from vinegar through it.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:19:23.629 --> 00:19:28.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Penicillin is a weakly acidic substance,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so it won't dissolve in acidic water.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:19:28.967 --> 00:19:32.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This will further remove</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any alkaline impurities.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:19:34.139 --> 00:19:38.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Finally, pass alkaline water</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with dissolved baking soda through it.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:19:38.544 --> 00:19:42.047 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This will cause the penicillin</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to dissolve out of the charcoal,</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:19:42.114 --> 00:19:45.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and you will get a high-purity</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>penicillin solution coming out from below.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:19:50.556 --> 00:19:52.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The extraction process is now complete.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:19:53.425 --> 00:19:57.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Next, we'll test the penicillin extract</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by dividing it into one-</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>shaku</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> portions</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:19:57.196 --> 00:19:59.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to test the drug's efficacy</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:19:59.831 --> 00:20:02.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why divide it into one-</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>shaku</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> portions?</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:20:02.634 --> 00:20:05.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the concentration of penicillin.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:20:05.170 --> 00:20:08.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We need to select a solution</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with an adequate concentration.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:20:08.607 --> 00:20:10.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is a medium made from agar.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:20:10.976 --> 00:20:15.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It has bacteria taken</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from syphilis patients smeared on it.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:20:15.881 --> 00:20:20.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Drop the penicillin extract onto this,</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:20:21.186 --> 00:20:23.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>cover it, and wait for a few days.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:20:23.222 --> 00:20:26.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If no changes occur</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the surface after a few days,</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:20:26.725 --> 00:20:29.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the penicillin solution</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is not working effectively.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:20:29.995 --> 00:20:33.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>On the other hand, if a circle</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>forms around the applied solution,</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:20:33.398 --> 00:20:36.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>it means that the penicillin</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has eradicated the bacteria.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:20:36.935 --> 00:20:41.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In other words, it means</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the penicillin solution is effective.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:20:48.547 --> 00:20:51.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now we can only pray to the heavens.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:20:53.218 --> 00:20:54.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:21:00.659 --> 00:21:04.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Does this really mean that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Sakamoto's desertion will be forgiven?</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:21:04.930 --> 00:21:06.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, this is the written promise for that.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:21:06.865 --> 00:21:07.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>AKASAKA, KATSU VILLA</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:21:07.966 --> 00:21:10.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I stopped by Shimoda,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a noble from Tosa came by,</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:21:10.702 --> 00:21:13.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>so I asked him to write it for me.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:21:13.205 --> 00:21:15.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if I were to have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my punishment revoked,</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:21:15.974 --> 00:21:17.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it wouldn't be such a big deal.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:21:18.377 --> 00:21:20.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But with this,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can openly train in the Navy.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:21:21.913 --> 00:21:22.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's how he is.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:21:23.715 --> 00:21:27.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>By the way, what is Dr. Minakata doing?</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:21:27.319 --> 00:21:31.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's at the Western Medicine School,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>making a medicine called penicillin.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:21:31.089 --> 00:21:34.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What kind of medicine is it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It should treat syphilis.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:21:34.926 --> 00:21:37.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He started making it at the request</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of a courtesan named Nokaze.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:21:37.963 --> 00:21:40.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The courtesan Nokaze?</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:21:40.198 --> 00:21:43.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If he can make something like that,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it will be quite spectacular.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:21:43.869 --> 00:21:47.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, Dr. Minakata always amazes me.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:21:50.842 --> 00:21:51.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:21:53.412 --> 00:21:56.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just when I thought</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I had finally made a step forward,</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:21:57.215 --> 00:21:59.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I find someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who's already several steps ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:22:00.886 --> 00:22:02.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Looking at that doctor,</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:22:03.422 --> 00:22:05.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't help but feel like a fool.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:22:25.310 --> 00:22:30.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When you smile,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it is like a breeze in spring.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:22:30.816 --> 00:22:32.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I remember people saying that.</i></c.bg_transparent>

278
00:22:33.318 --> 00:22:37.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The road was overflowing with visitors,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>hoping to catch a glimpse of that.</i></c.bg_transparent>

279
00:22:39.091 --> 00:22:43.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You were my pride.</i></c.bg_transparent>

280
00:22:47.999 --> 00:22:52.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>But soon, you could</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>no longer work in the brothel.</i></c.bg_transparent>

281
00:22:53.138 --> 00:22:56.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Thanks to the support of those</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>who were your customers,</i></c.bg_transparent>

282
00:22:56.308 --> 00:22:59.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I was able to become the next </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Yobidashi</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>.</i></c.bg_transparent>

283
00:23:01.346 --> 00:23:03.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I thought for sure</i></c.bg_transparent>

284
00:23:03.181 --> 00:23:06.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>you would say something unpleasant to me.</i></c.bg_transparent>

285
00:23:12.090 --> 00:23:13.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did well.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:23:16.328 --> 00:23:22.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My savings are depleted,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I can only offer this, but…</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:23:23.335 --> 00:23:26.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Say whatever you want to say.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:23:27.606 --> 00:23:31.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you keep everything bottled up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without saying a word of resentment,</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:23:33.211 --> 00:23:35.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it won't be good for your health.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:23:40.085 --> 00:23:40.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well then…</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:23:44.623 --> 00:23:46.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>whether you cry or laugh,</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:23:48.493 --> 00:23:50.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it's all one lifetime.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:23:52.297 --> 00:23:53.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, in this lifetime,</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:23:56.435 --> 00:23:57.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't cry.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:24:02.607 --> 00:24:06.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please remember this.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:24:09.781 --> 00:24:10.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:24:20.992 --> 00:24:24.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please smile, sister.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:24:26.431 --> 00:24:31.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was you who told me to smile.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:24:38.176 --> 00:24:39.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ouch…</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:24:43.548 --> 00:24:45.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Found some, even at a place like that.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:25:01.800 --> 00:25:02.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tomorrow…</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:25:18.116 --> 00:25:21.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the medicine is effective,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there will be a circle on the surface.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:25:22.254 --> 00:25:26.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, if there are no changes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>visible on the surface,</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:25:27.158 --> 00:25:28.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the medicine is not effective.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:25:29.961 --> 00:25:32.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Then, let's open them.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Please do.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:25:46.511 --> 00:25:47.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Number one.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:25:49.080 --> 00:25:50.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not effective.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:25:59.991 --> 00:26:00.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Number two.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:26:02.460 --> 00:26:03.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not effective.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:26:08.033 --> 00:26:09.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Number three</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:26:10.969 --> 00:26:12.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not effective.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:26:13.171 --> 00:26:16.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miki, please,</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:26:17.509 --> 00:26:18.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Number four.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:26:18.977 --> 00:26:20.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not effective.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:26:29.955 --> 00:26:30.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Number eight.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:26:31.623 --> 00:26:32.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not effective.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:26:35.126 --> 00:26:36.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Number nine.</c.bg_transparent>

